REST Services with Spring and JPA

This repo contains the implementation for this project:
https://www.manning.com/liveprojectseries/design-implement-rest-services-spring-jpa

and is organized in 6 subprojects, each one contained in a dedicated branch.

The project covers the following topics:
- containerize Java Spring Boot app using docker and docker compose
- connect to database using Spring Data JPA and TestContainers for database integration test
- implement Rest service and generate a SwaggerUI and OpenApi documentation with SpringDoc
- implement queries using JPQL
- implement back office service using ActiveMQ Artemis
- implement authorization for the API using Spring Security and OAuth 2.0 authentication

Run the app (run_maven.sh or run_gradle.sh) then open this page for manual testing and documentation

http://127.0.0.1:8080/swagger-ui/index.html